Troubleshooting Tips
Common Issues and Solutions
Issue: Permission denied when accessing log files Solution: Use sudo for system log access or check file permissions

Issue: Scripts not executing Solution: Ensure scripts have execute permissions using chmod +x script_name.sh

Issue: High CPU usage persists Solution: Use pkill -f yes to terminate all instances of the yes command

Issue: Cannot find created files Solution: Verify you're in the correct directory using pwd and ls -la

Issue: Network monitoring shows no connections Solution: Some services may not be running; this is normal in a lab environment

